{"tid":614012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南生圍縱火案關注TG Group","createTime":"2018-04-02T07:14:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T07:46:54.000Z","uid":5984,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3d6da723a124bbf7ce1c695c2c8778b3eca0f6fd","tid":614012,"uid":5984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:14:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180402/s00001/1522630923724\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180402%2Fs00001%2F1522630923724&d=WRjTCwRdf2gXWummLCWADfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=2a678292\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180402%2Fs00001%2F1522630923724&h=dcd871f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180402/s00001/1522630923724</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南生圍再遭縱火　橫水渡碼頭木船燒毁<br />\n<br />\n元朗南生圍再發生縱火案。清晨6時許，一艘泊在南生圍橫水渡碼頭的木船被發現冒煙起火，消防接報到場將火救熄，無人受傷，經調查後初步相信起火原因有可疑，列作「縱火」處理，交由警方跟進。<br />\n<br />\n橫水渡碼頭每日由清晨6時至晚上11時提供服務，木船接載市民前往山貝村碼頭。<br />\n<br />\n上月南生圍接連發生兩宗火警，警方將兩案暫列縱火，交由重案組跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁樣燒法真係無法無天，但政府完全坐視不理。<br />\n有無人想搞返個TG group集思廣益點集自己少少嘅力量去幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留低你嘅TG一齊加入，唔好再坐係電腦面前做鍵盤戰士喇"},{"pid":"412f2db6915cd4fe625e49f9ca8aea5bdeccf8a4","tid":614012,"uid":31215,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:55:22.000Z","msg":"組民兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e340ba61d0f37507673b9880f43312443fe751c1","tid":614012,"uid":103127,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T07:58:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"437027be66c4f4214ffcf5ce2516e066fe51ff13","tid":614012,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:15:18.000Z","msg":"推，集思廣益下點樣可以保護到南生圍"},{"pid":"cb74071019af27fe2e1f6afdec588f4b01b27c60","tid":614012,"uid":5984,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:51:37.000Z","msg":"大家唔好齋推 留低TG開個Group從長計議啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f69956e4d7f9c94a42991e5357549b2d4fcde7","tid":614012,"uid":5984,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:51:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aacf620b70297c0f7e34cf7dc5d67480e7a0d89d","tid":614012,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T08:57:12.000Z","msg":"MONEY FIRST"},{"pid":"a581b44d11e5c25f6a595f3e1610a7633125ef56","tid":614012,"uid":5984,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:03:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc9733ce62742cc28a72c260f8ae41ee753120ba","tid":614012,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:04:12.000Z","msg":"link？"},{"pid":"cef3285427fcf20a2605f2af48487716e94f41b6","tid":614012,"uid":5984,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"cc9733ce62742cc28a72c260f8ae41ee753120ba","tid":614012,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:04:12.000Z","msg":"link？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:14:57.000Z","msg":"而家得ching你一個 <br />\n多啲人先開group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"572fd26dac8aa52bbad3d0cc57b5f10ceff466a6","tid":614012,"uid":5984,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:43:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffddf23294be24a8e4014d48e2740a31e42928ab","tid":614012,"uid":5984,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:43:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"732ace8a40efa29a6910115a1aebdadb88037389","tid":614012,"uid":5984,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T10:43:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67203507101b166649274ba573220b1ae444d4